(804, 'Gimme All Your Lovin\'', 'Eliminator (1983)', 'I got to have a shot of what you got is oh so sweet.\r\nYou got to make it hot, like a boomerang I need a repeat,\r\n\r\nGimme all your lovin\', all your hugs and kisses too,\r\nGimme all your lovin\', don\'t let up until we\'re through,\r\n\r\nYou got to whip it up and hit me like a ton of lead,\r\nIf I blow my top will you let it go to your head?\r\n\r\nGimme all your lovin\', all your hugs and kisses too,\r\nGimme all your lovin\', don\'t let up until we\'re through.\r\n\r\nYou got to move it up and use it like a schoolboy would.\r\nYou got to pack it up, work it like a new boy should.\r\n\r\nGimme all your lovin\', all your hugs and kisses too.\r\nGimme all your lovin\', don\'t let up until we\'re through.\r\n\r\n- Billy Gibbons, Dusty Hill & Frank Beard', 'ZZ Top', album.jpg, '2024-10-15 17:41:49', '2024-10-15 17:41:49', 'ZZ Top', 0),
(805, 'For Once In My Life', 'For Once In My Life', 'For once in my life I have someone who needs me\r\nSomeone I\'ve needed so long\r\nFor once, unafraid, I can go where life leads me\r\nAnd somehow I know I\'ll be strong\r\n\r\nFor once I can touch what my heart used to dream of\r\nLong before I knew\r\nSomeone warm like you\r\nWould make my dreams come true\r\n\r\nFor once in my life I won\'t let sorrow hurt me\r\nNot like it\'s hurt me before\r\nFor once, I have something I know won\'t desert me\r\nI\'m not alone anymore\r\n\r\nFor once, I can say, this is mine, you can\'t take it\r\nAs long as I know I have love, I can make it\r\nFor once in my life, I have someone who needs me', 'Stevie Wonder', album.jpg, '2024-10-15 17:42:11', '2024-10-15 17:42:11', 'Stevie Wonder', 0),
